                  <summary><title type="supplied">Sagas of Apostles</title><note>AM 628 4to is one of three copies
                        of <title type="ms">Codex Scardensis</title> (<ref type="ms"
                           target="#SAM02-0001-is">SÁM 1</ref>) commissioned by Árni Magnússon and
                        written in Iceland 1710-1712 by Eyjólfur Björnsson. Eyjólfur's copies are
                        now preserved as<ref type="ms" target="#AM04-0628-en">AM 628 4to</ref>, AM
                        631 4to and <ref type="ms" target="#AM04-0636-is">AM 636 4to</ref>.</note>
                  </summary>
